    "name": "Bondi Backpackers Nha Trang",
    "detail": "Very clean, good location. The gal who works the desk in the morning and her brother who is there overnight are incredibly helpful. The gal in the afternoon and evening, not so much. We had a private room and bathroom on the 6th floor. The private suite did not come with handsoap or a hand towel and we were only given 1 bath towel which was a bit strange. AC works well. Unfortunately there is no safe, nowhere to hang a clothes line and limited hooks to hang wet things in the bathroom. One night there were a bunch of backpackers being very noisy on the roof until 1230am. Also, the big bummer is that the pool was under maintenance our entire stay. Overall, we liked it here and even stayed a few extra nights. If we are back in Nha Trang again, we would definitely stay here",
